narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's a lot of fun! Take it! I took it on a whim and it was the most fun I had in any course all semester. You get credit for chatting about yourself and your life with people!
Too much, too quickly for people just starting the language. It was pretty tough to keep up.
French is a good course and a great language, so if they are willing to put in the time and effort, then I would recommend it.
Yes, the course was well organized and student will learn not only language but also tons of opportunities to in touch with French culture through the class
